Welcome to Zombie Survival: Endless Night, an intense and never-ending action game where your only goal is simple — survive for as long as you can.

You are trapped in an endless cycle of terror. Hordes of zombies are coming at you from all directions, and there’s no way out. Armed with only your gun and your reflexes, you must shoot down the undead before they get to you.

But be careful:
⚠️ Every time a zombie touches you, you lose 10 HP.
❤️ You start with 100 HP, so once it’s gone — it’s game over.

How long can you last before you’re overwhelmed?
How many zombies can you take down before they take you?

This is an IVY RPG GAME MASTER by Jacky

FOLLOW THE GUIDE BELOW TO UNDERSTAND HOW TO PLAY:

> use your arrow keys to move the blue player.

> you can enter inside the buildings in the game by going close to the door.

> you can interact with items around by going close to it and pressing the "space bar"

> the red player behind your house is a crafts man, so if you want to craft an item you can go close to him and interact with him

> follow the brown road to move the next place where you will see IVY STORES (a place you can buy and sell items by going close to the seller to interact with him) and also be aware of the IVY SPRITES, they can pop up any time there

> use the key "i" to show your inventory and you can remove it by clicking "i"- if it doesnt work click "i" multiple times

> use the key "a" to spun a weapon ball to attack the IVY sprites and earn money (IN ALL YOU DO TRY TO AVOID THEM HITTING YOU UNLESS YOU WILL LOSE YOUR HEALTH) 

AND NOT TO FORGET, I MADE IT THAT YOU CANT DIE SO THAT YOU WILL ENJOY THE GAME EVEN MORE

THANK YOU AND ENJOY YOUR GAME

THANKS IVY TEAM FOR THE OPPORTUNITY

🦀 Scaredy Crab – How Far Can You Go?
Meet the crab who's terrified of bugs—and there's only one way out: JUMP.
Time your spacebar hits just right and help Scaredy Crab leap over the creepy crawling insect closing in fast.

Sounds easy? Think again.
Can you survive 15 jumps? That’s the mark of someone who’s at least got reflexes.

Make it to 30? You’re a legend.
Push past that? You're knocking on the gates of crab-god status 🏆
No second chances. No mercy. Just you, the spacebar, and your crabby instincts.

Play now and prove you're not just food for the bugs.
Let’s see who jumps… and who panics.

In Slippery No More, snowflakes are falling fast, turning the basketball court into a dangerous ice rink. If you don’t act, the ballers could slip, crash, and get seriously hurt.

Grab your bowl and jump into the action! Catch every flake before it hits the ground and save the court from becoming a frozen hazard. The more flakes you catch, the safer the players stay—but miss one and the game is over.

This isn’t just a game, it’s a mission. Are you quick enough to keep the court dry and the ballers safe?
